snippet.title: SkySaga - Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Introducing SkySaga, the world of infinite possibilities. 

Gear up for unique journeys with limitless horizons, building and crafting to shape the world around you. 
Claim treasures and conquer enemies alone or as a team. 
Achieve victory in dungeon quests and tactical PvP. 

SkySaga is your story, how will you tell it?

Sign up at http://skysa.ga/YTRegisterNow for your chance to play!

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/SkySaga
Twitter: https://twitter.com/SkySaga
Forum: https://forum.skysaga.com/
Watch live at http://www.twitch.tv/skysagagame

Please note that SkySaga is currently in Closed Alpha, so all content seen here is subject to change.
